Add To Every object
  Is Not carried.
End Add.

Add To Every actor
  Container
End Add.

The l Isa location
  Initialize
		FOR EACH ac ISA ACTOR 
			DO
				IF THIS <> hero
					THEN
						IF COUNT ISA OBJECT, DIRECTLY IN ac > 0
							THEN 
								FOR EACH o ISA OBJECT, IN ac
									DO
										MAKE o carried.
								END FOR.
						END IF.
				END IF.
		END FOR.						
End The l.

Start At l.
